. Ok, I have a workarround:

Instead of using ".setItems" use a simple ListView with a ArrayAdapter:

```
HoloAlertDialogBuilder dialogBuilder = new HoloAlertDialogBuilder(this);

    ListView modeList = new ListView(getActivity());
    String[] stringArray = new String[] { "Bright Mode", "Normal Mode" };
